column5: I finally had the time to hit some different lakes, so that's what my Dad and I did.  Tough guys lip their Lakers.
Thats a tank walleye!  Must have came out of deep water I guess?
Looks like a great day on the ice . Nice walleye !!!
NICE.. fishing with Dad! The fish ain't bad either...
You guys able to sled on the lake or just walking out?  Nice fish. The walleye especially
Wow. Some great fishing.  You can totally lip your walleye. I'll show you when we hang out. (bring band-aids)
NICE!   I'll lip a walleye........ With pliers
Congrats Chris your on your game for sure Have u done your tournament yet  u will be a contender for sure
looks like you caught that eye on a slice of tomato
Fish come and go each day. That what you watched with the otter. PRICELESS.  Nice day there bud.
Always loved fishing with my dad,that was always the best part.Great photos Chris !!!
Looks like you had a great outing with your Dad Chris nice chunky walleye.
